snippet.title: Best VGM 2407 - Monster Boy and the Cursed Kingdom - Misty Woods
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Switch / PS4 / XB1
Monster Boy and the Cursed Kingdom (2018)
Misty Woods
Yuzo Koshiro
